   <div class="teaser_fmt"> 
    <h3>Eye Health Overview</h3> 
    <p>Regular eye exams reveal vision problems like nearsightedness, farsightedness, presbyopia, and astigmatism. Your doctor may prescribe glasses or contact lenses. Eye conditions include pinkeye, blepharitis, glaucoma, cataracts, and macular degeneration.</p> 
