   <div class="article_snippet_rdr">
    <h3>A Visit to the Eye Doctor</h3>
    <div class="snippet_fmt" id="asnip">
     <p xmlns:xalan="http://xml.apache.org/xalan">Think you don't need to see an eye doctor because your vision is fine? Think again.</p>
     <p xmlns:xalan="http://xml.apache.org/xalan">Eye exams aren’t only for people with poor vision. They're an important way of detecting eye problems before you have symptoms. Eye doctors can also catch other health problems -- like diabetes -- early.&nbsp;</p>
    </div>
